The application of the present invention will be described with respect to a method for issuing community tax certificates and other relevant permits and clearances as a digital certificate, using verifiable credentials, digital wallet on a blockchain as payment provision, and machine learning.
Claim 1: A method for issuing a community tax certificate and other permits and clearances as a digital certificate, using verifiable credentials, digital wallet on a blockchain as payment provision, and machine learning, comprising the steps of:
(a) receiving an application for a community tax certificate and other permits and clearances;
(b) authenticating the applicant’s identity using biometric data;
(c) determining if the applicant is eligible for the community tax certificate and other permits and clearances based on predefined criteria;
(d) generating a verifiable credential for the applicant that includes information about the community tax certificate and other permits and clearances;
(e) storing the verifiable credential in a blockchain;
(f) providing payment for the community tax certificate and other permits and clearances using a digital wallet on a blockchain;
(g) utilizing machine learning to detect fraudulent applications;
(h) issuing the community tax certificate and other permits and clearances to the applicant upon successful completion of the above steps.
Claim 2: The method of claim 1, further comprising the step of:
(i) providing a digital wallet on a blockchain for payment provision.
